  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2519010/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.poster.avif?t=1727667419\" width=591 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2519010/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.webm?t=1727667419\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hey everyone! Just a heads up - I'm still tweaking and improving the game, and I love hearing your ideas. Feel free to drop any suggestions in the community hub or shoot them over on Discord. Your input really helps shape the game, so keep them coming!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2519010/extras/4aa747166c32bafe1603b2171e14e0a9.webp?t=1727667419\" width=600 height=56 /></span>In this game, we've flipped the script on the classic Snake game. Instead of controlling the snake, you're the fruit! Your goal is to evade the relentless snake in a thrilling game of cat and mouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2519010/extras/7068b111c27498a1da014083f1cca4f0.webp?t=1727667419\" width=600 height=56 /></span>The real challenge lies not just in surviving, but in outdoing yourself and others. Collect points to climb the leaderboard and prove your skill. Every game is a new opportunity to reach the top!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2519010/extras/db68a04bf2e11401c45e881b36864d10.webp?t=1727667419\" width=600 height=56 /></span>This isn't just a game of chance. It's a test of your skill and tactical prowess. Points increase each time the snake devours an apple, so you'll need to think on your feet and make every move count. </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2519010/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.poster.avif?t=1727667419\" width=591 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2519010/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.webm?t=1727667419\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hey everyone! Just a heads up - I'm still tweaking and improving the game, and I love hearing your ideas. Feel free to drop any suggestions in the community hub or shoot them over on Discord. Your input really helps shape the game, so keep them coming!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2519010/extras/4aa747166c32bafe1603b2171e14e0a9.webp?t=1727667419\" width=600 height=56 /></span>In this game, we've flipped the script on the classic Snake game. Instead of controlling the snake, you're the fruit! Your goal is to evade the relentless snake in a thrilling game of cat and mouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2519010/extras/7068b111c27498a1da014083f1cca4f0.webp?t=1727667419\" width=600 height=56 /></span>The real challenge lies not just in surviving, but in outdoing yourself and others. Collect points to climb the leaderboard and prove your skill. Every game is a new opportunity to reach the top!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2519010/extras/db68a04bf2e11401c45e881b36864d10.webp?t=1727667419\" width=600 height=56 /></span>This isn't just a game of chance. It's a test of your skill and tactical prowess. Points increase each time the snake devours an apple, so you'll need to think on your feet and make every move count. </p>",
